headline.main: Japan's Emperor Pays Respects to Thailand's Late King
headline.print_headline: Japan's Emperor Pays Respects to Thailand's Late King

lead_paragraph: Japanese Emperor Akihito paid his respects to the late Thai King Bhumibol Adulyadej on Sunday, arriving in Bangkok following a weeklong trip to Vietnam aimed at winning support against Chinese expansionism.
